{"tid":1463932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要］建議成立臨時機場糾察，控制失控示威者、或者鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:05:39.000Z","uid":99956,"like":4,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc1ed7ec4642aab653ae8482255b876a49c087c","tid":1463932,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:04:51.000Z","msg":"睇立場有條友係咁煽動其他人，又打立場記者，真係覺得好鬼，明明一直強調「和理飛」，塞機場係一個重要既牌，我地唔可以失，一陣暴力又比位人地入，呢家和平塞又阻到飛機同埋可以向外國人傳遞訊息，一舉多得，因為我地行為和平，政府同警察更加無藉口政入黎！<br />\n<br />\n建議成立臨時糾察，一見到失控既人就上者阻止，甚至趕佢地走，唔好比佢地搞事，令到我地失去機場呢一手牌！"},{"pid":"b4cebebfd6bdc829a02b211fbf57cbbc818e36dc","tid":1463932,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bed087b1f27e41226657f6849958cb02eb01398","tid":1463932,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4ef39f579b4c5bf5d843585726dc1a57a1f57e4","tid":1463932,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05224c1cc73d8e1964aea11bb18e0295f22db125","tid":1463932,"uid":2002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:48.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"1272729192c97ced50cc132eebe669b7213ed1d8","tid":1463932,"uid":99956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02980b4cbefd757d66f9449c5111fcdcf78531fb","tid":1463932,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span>"},{"pid":"07fc71f4412a33592552422f7a4a702d0f2b9ed2","tid":1463932,"uid":72693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"